# input
sudo nft add rule inet fw4 input tcp dport 443 counter drop
sudo nft add rule inet fw4 input udp dport 443 counter drop

# forward
sudo nft add rule inet fw4 forward tcp dport 443 counter drop
sudo nft add rule inet fw4 forward udp dport 443 counter drop

